            UI/UX Design – Led by Devajit Mutsuddy
        <p class="desc-box-2">
            Devajit led the UI/UX design of NoteRoom, ensuring that the platform’s interface was intuitive and visually appealing. He developed wireframes and prototypes using Figma to map out the user journey and structure the platform’s layout. His work included creating a consistent design system, which defined the color schemes, typography, icons, and other visual elements, ensuring a cohesive look and feel across the platform. Devajit also worked closely with the frontend developers, including Anirban, to ensure the designs were accurately implemented and reflected the intended user experience.</p>
